title: The Haves and the Have Nots S04E05 (Aired July 19, 2016)
description: The Haves and the Have Nots is a prime time cable Drama Show writer by Tyler Perry, focusing on the interacting lives of the Rich Cryer&Harrington families, and the poor Young family. Hanna Young, a have not maid working for the Cryers, is a woman(Who Is Not Perfect)And Used To Be A Backslider,But Now is a woman of faith. But her faith, and her resolve are tested when she finds out that her Promiscuous Daughter Candace Young(To Whom She Trys To Unattach Her From)has Interwoven Herself into the lives of her Mothers employer Jim Cryer and his Family
